text: Lee Soo-hyun () is a Korean name consisting of the family name Lee and the given name Soo-hyun, and may also refer to: * Lee Su-hyun (singer, born 1996), South Korean singer and a member of I.B.I * Lee Su-hyun (singer, born 1999), South Korean singer and a member of Akdong Musician
title: Lee Su-hyun
